title: "Meta Ads"
abstract: >
  Meta paid advertising audit and optimization skill conforming to the Agent
  Skills open standard. Verified on Claude Code / Cowork. Covers Facebook,
  Instagram, Reels, Threads, Messenger, and Audience Network under the
  Advantage+ / Andromeda / GEM / Lattice delivery stack — including Entity-ID
  clustering prediction — with 130+ audit checks, 15 sub-skills, 9 parallel
  agents, 12 industry templates, Pixel/CAPI + EMQ and Conversions API
  server-side tracking deep dives, Meta attribution analysis, PPC math, A/B
  test design, PDF report generation, and a pytest eval harness.
